CREATE procedure [dbo].[tmp_insupd_test_step] @t_test_id uniqueidentifier
as 
UPDATE [dbo].[T_TEST_STEP]
   SET [STEP_NUM] = t2.STEP_NUM,
      [STEP_ORDER] = t2.STEP_ORDER,
      [PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1] = t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1,
      [PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2] = t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2,
      [PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3] = t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3,

      [T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID] = t2.T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID,
      [ACTUAL_MARK] = t2.ACTUAL_MARK
 from t_test_step t1 
 inner join tmp_t_test_step t2 on t1.t_test_step_id = t2.t_test_step_id 
 WHERE t2.t_test_id = @t_test_id

ScalarOperator.@ScalarString: CASE WHEN [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[ACTUAL_MARK]<>'n' AND [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[ACTUAL_MARK]<>'y' THEN (0) ELSE NULL END

[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_NUM] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_NUM] as [t2].[STEP_NUM],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_ORDER] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_ORDER] as [t2].[STEP_ORDER],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1] as [t2].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2] as [t2].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3] as [t2].[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID] as [t2].[T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID],[PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[ACTUAL_MARK] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[ACTUAL_MARK] as [t2].[ACTUAL_MARK]
CASE WHEN [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_NUM] as [t1].[STEP_NUM] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_NUM] as [t2].[STEP_NUM] THEN (1) ELSE (0) END
CASE WHEN [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_ORDER] as [t1].[STEP_ORDER] = [PSYCHOLOGY_TEST_1].[dbo].[TMP_T_TEST_STEP].[STEP_ORDER] as [t2].[STEP_ORDER] THEN (1) ELSE (0) END
CASE WHEN [Expr1022] IS NULL THEN (0) ELSE NULL END

INSERT INTO [dbo].[T_TEST_STEP]
           ([STEP_NUM]
           ,[OBJ_CREATED]
           ,[OBJ_CREATED_BY]
           ,[STEP_ORDER]
           ,[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1]
           ,[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2]
           ,[PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3]
           ,[T_TEST_ID]
           ,[T_TEST_STEP_ID]
           ,[T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID]
           ,[ACTUAL_MARK])
select 
           t2.STEP_NUM,
           getdate(),
           t2.OBJ_CREATED_BY,
           t2.STEP_ORDER,
           t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG1,
           t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG2,
           t2.PAGE_USR_TEXT_LANG3,
           t2.T_TEST_ID,
           t2.T_TEST_STEP_ID,
	   t2.T_TEST_STEP_JS_FILE_ID,
           t2.ACTUAL_MARK
from tmp_t_test_step t2 
where t2.t_test_id = @t_test_id 
and t2.t_test_step_id not in (
select t1.t_test_step_id from t_test_step t1 
)
